        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Carbon Cost Act of 2024&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This bill requires the Government Accountability Office to coordinate with the National Academy of Sciences to study alternatives for a nonpartisan congressional office or agency to make science-based projections of the effect of federal legislation on global greenhouse gas emissions.&lt;/p&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
      </summary>
